# Task Manager App

A cross-platform mobile application that helps users organize daily tasks efficiently with priorities, deadlines, and reminders. The app features a clean UI and supports offline usage with local storage.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Add, edit, and delete tasks
- Set task priorities
- Add deadlines and reminders
- Offline support
- Data stored locally using AsyncStorage

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- React Native
- JavaScript
- AsyncStorage

---

## 📱 About the App
This Task Manager App is designed to improve productivity by helping users track and manage their daily activities in a simple and organized way. It works offline and ensures data is always saved locally on the device.

---

## 📌 Future Improvements
- Cloud sync support
- Push notifications
- Dark mode
- Task categories

---

